Hello,

This email message is a notification to let you know that
a file has been uploaded to the Files area of the neat 
group.

  File        : /NEAT.tar.bz2 
  Uploaded by : petar_chervenski <petar_chervenski@...> 
  Description : My implementation of NEAT, rtNEAT and Novelty Search. Has Python bindings (needs boost::python and boost::serialization). For Genome visualition OpenCV 2.3 with Python bindings is required. This is the first release and may have bugs and ommited code.  

You can access this file at the URL:
http://groups.yahoo.com/group/neat/files/NEAT.tar.bz2
